textContent: I've been wanting you to show me how much you want to be together with more active engagement. Instead it feels like you pull back and don't engage. I read this as you're not sure. And then I ask if I'm projecting my own thoughts. Have I showed you every day how resolved I am in our relationship? Have we had conversations that light up our eyes and find joy in each other's answers? Have we made the space and the time to continue to listen and ask questions? Maybe I am just as aloof because I feel like you haven't really gotten to know me. And I imagine you may feel the same way
